Display game title heading

Make start button to begin game

Display question 1

Make clickable buttons of four possible answers for each question.

Display Timer with a countdown from 30 seconds to 0

If the user clicks on the correct answer, display "Correct! The answer is: " plus the correct answer and display correct answer picture.

Else if the user clicks on any of the other answers, display "Nope! The correct answer is: " plus the correct answer and display correct answer picture.

If the timer gets to zero before the user clicks on a button, display "Out of Time! The correct answer is: " plus the correct answer and display picture.

Wait 3 seconds and then go to the next question.

After the final question, display the total of correct answers, total of incorrect answers, and a button to restart the game.

